       <header class="entry-header">
        <h1 class="entry-title">
         Top 10 Free Android Games in November 2014
        </h1>
        <div class="below-title-meta">
         <div class="adt">
          By
          <span class="author">
           <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/author/foreseequiz/" rel="author" title="Posts by foreseequiz">
            foreseequiz
           </a>
          </span>
          <span class="meta-sep">
           |
          </span>
          November 26, 2014
         </div>
         <div class="adt-comment">
          <a class="link-comments" href="http://foreseequiz.com/top-10-free-android-games-november-2014/#comments">
           0 Comment
          </a>
         </div>
        </div>
        <!-- below title meta end -->
       </header>
       <!-- .entry-header -->
       <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="fb-social-plugin fb-like" data-href="http://foreseequiz.com/top-10-free-android-games-november-2014/" data-ref="above-post" data-width="650">
        </div>
        <p>
         The contribution of smartphones to gaming is well recognized. This arena is becoming more and more interesting day by day. There are tonnes of games on the Play Store. In this blog, I will present the top ten games that you can try this month.
        </p>
        <p>
         1.
         <strong>
          Daddy Long Legs
         </strong>
          The game plot is simple. You have to walk as far as you can. Your legs are way bigger than your body. So, walking can be a tough job. Put one leg in front of the other and try not to fall down. Just tap on the screen to make the big daddy stagger on the screen.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Daddy-Long-Legs.jpg">
          <img alt="Daddy Long Legs" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-637" height="225" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Daddy-Long-Legs-300x225.jpg" width="300"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="https://lh3.ggpht.com/lf6-jVXtUlcrTojaqkJ4s-Bf0snKlfsap2hFOaACLzd2u83njg5f9VzWviRvW-sD=h900">
          Image Source:
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         2.
         <strong>
          Counterspy
         </strong>
          A cold war is going on between The World and a superpower. The superpower is about to start a nuclear strike on the world. You have to stop this superpower from launching the attack, but surreptitiously. You are an agent of C.O.U.N.T.E.R. and being an agent, you need to jump into action, sabotage devastating plans and save the World!
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Counterspy.jpg">
          <img alt="Counterspy" class="alignnone wp-image-638" height="174" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Counterspy.jpg" width="311"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
          Image Source:
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         3.
         <strong>
          Phantom Rift
         </strong>
          The Phantom Rift is a dark ghostly world filled with mystery and powerful magic. You dont know the reason of your presence there, but, you have to return back to the real world at any cost. Phantom Rift is an adventure/RPG with a remarkable battle system, hundreds of spells to gather and use, endless equipment combinations to characterize your skills with, and much more.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Phantom-Rift.jpg">
          <img alt="Phantom Rift" class="alignnone wp-image-639" height="175" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Phantom-Rift.jpg" width="311"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://images.mob.org/androidgame_img/phantom_rift/real/1_phantom_rift.jpg">
          Image Source:
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         4.
         <strong>
          NFL Quarterback 15
         </strong>
          In this game, you are a NFL quarterback. Choose your favourite team and hop into the toughest challenge on the field. The controls are short, moves are pretty smooth and the graphics are just amazing!
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/NFL-Quarterback-15.jpg">
          <img alt="NFL Quarterback 15" class="alignnone wp-image-640" height="166" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/NFL-Quarterback-15-300x157.jpg" width="317"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="https://fbexternal-a.akamaihd.net/safe_image.php?d=AQDm44BRxIxcJ9dm&amp;w=470&amp;h=246&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Bon2-xfIu2I%2FVAuRu3-dIdI%2FAAAAAAAAKEQ%2FAtnTZa3rW1c%2Fs1600%2FNFL%252BQuarterback%252B15%252BAPK%252B0.jpg&amp;cfs=1&amp;upscale=1">
          Image Source:
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         5.
         <strong>
          The Inquisitor  Book 1
         </strong>
          This game will enable you to play a character who has a will of steel, a heart of stone, a sharp intelligence and lots of wisdom. And, above all, you get tonnes of fancy divine weapons to resist the evil.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/The-Inquisitor--Book-1.jpg">
          <img alt="The Inquisitor  Book 1" class="alignnone wp-image-641" height="178" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/The-Inquisitor--Book-1-300x165.jpg" width="324"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://www.lucasbenaglia.it/images/androidgameimage_stu/sbenny.com_The_Inquisitor_Book1.jpg">
          Image Source:
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         6.
         <strong>
          Skull Legends
         </strong>
          You are a fighter. Fight against the tiny bony creatures with nothing but your boney acquiesce. The game also contains tower defense style turrets with a shooting gallery, with more powerful weapons. Be careful of the in-app purchases.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Skull-Legends.jpg">
          <img alt="Skull Legends" class="alignnone wp-image-642" height="184" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Skull-Legends.jpg" width="329"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://images.mob.org/androidgame_img/skull_legends/real/1_skull_legends.jpg">
          Image Source:
         </a>
         <br/>
         7.
         <strong>
          Heli Hell
         </strong>
          Your fighter chopper and you  tear the sky apart with the deadly combination. You are here to save the world from evil forces who want to capture your land. You come across Dr. Evil and his squadrons on an island called Vyllena. Your job is to trace him out and demolish all his hostile activities before its too late.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Heli-Hell.jpg">
          <img alt="Heli Hell" class="alignnone wp-image-643" height="171" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Heli-Hell-300x135.jpg" width="380"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://static.androidgame365.com/uploads/posts/2014-09/1410141581_heli-hell.jpg">
          Image Source:
         </a>
         <br/>
         8.
         <strong>
          Hyper Trip
         </strong>
          Lot of physics are involved in this game. This is a reflex game and is set in an ultra-modern 3D neon-lit environment, where you have to guide a square by tapping left or right on the screen. You have to aim for an ideal pace of movement by avoiding hitting a wall.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Hyper-Trip.jpg">
          <img alt="Hyper Trip" class="alignnone wp-image-644" height="211" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Hyper-Trip.jpg" width="376"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://images.pocketgamer.co.uk/images/featimgs/best-3-droid-sep-12-hyper-trip.jpg">
          Image Source:
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         9.
         <strong>
          Desert Golfing
         </strong>
          Sand and only sand. Is there any escape from the sand? You might have to experience the next hole to know the answer!
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Desert-Golfing.png">
          <img alt="Desert Golfing" class="alignnone wp-image-645" height="208" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Desert-Golfing-300x169.png" width="369"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="https://lh3.ggpht.com/CPpc5rXNafRMwWwqny5AOKQKXu3LxIxsUangOhcFGy9Xjs88uhT7rycKugoyLf9dQmY=h900">
          Image Source:
         </a>
         <br/>
         10.
         <strong>
          Super Monkey Ball Bounce
         </strong>
          Trace your way through jungles, volcanoes and glaciers by bouncing, sliding and rebounding to rescue your monkey friends. It is also a multiplayer game. You can also collect international high scores.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Super-Monkey-Ball-Bounce.jpg">
          <img alt="Super Monkey Ball Bounce" class="alignnone wp-image-646" height="247" src="http://foreseequiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Super-Monkey-Ball-Bounce.jpg" width="371"/>
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         <a href="http://gamemob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/monkey-ball.jpg">
          Image Source:
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
        </p>
